actions_taken.summary:
The Azerbaijan Red Crescent Society (AzRC) has been taking initial preparedness steps with further potential and possible response focusing the areas: 
‚Ä¢	MHPSS support, especially for people coming from south the border of Azerbaijan namely Lenkeran, Astara, Bilasuvar;
‚Ä¢	First Aid services for people on the move;
‚Ä¢	Provision of food and water, to cover immediate basic needs;
‚Ä¢	Ongoing needs assessment, to track the evolving situation and identify any additional support required.
The AzRC has already initiated cooperation with relevant government bodies in cities located near the border. According to the local Emergency Situations authority, they are currently in full control of the situation and managing the response efforts on the ground. They have noted that support from the Red Crescent will be requested if and when additional assistance is required.
